%F A014846 a(n) = 5*a(n-1) - 9*a(n-2) + 7*a(n-3) - 2*a(n-4); a(1)=0, a(2)=-1, a(3)=a(4)=-2. - _Harvey P. Dale_, Aug 02 2011
%F A014846 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, Apr 01 2026: (Start)
%F A014846 O.g.f.: -x^2*(x^2 - 3*x + 1)/((2*x - 1)*(x - 1)^3).
%F A014846 E.g.f.: -(1 + x*(x + 2)*exp(x) - exp(2*x))/2. (End)
